I cannot express how much I love Amputee Mountain. This is the best doujin I've ever read and I don't think I'll ever read anything as beautiful. There's so much this doujin offers that goes beyond even the best of 'normal' manga. With just 29 pages, soooo much is conveyed. It has the soothing atmospheric that invites you into this strange world they inhabit. You can feel the undulating sun casting long shadows on the forest. The thin air that the sisters struggle to force their way through and unconfortable angles reminiscent of dutch angles that convey the discomfort and hastiness the sisters experience by traversing a land they aren't familiar with. The cat who by the end almost cutesy`-ly snuggles up to the leg of the grandma. The juxtaposition between the heinous events and the cute actions of the cat reveal its lack of empathy to the sisters. It isn't evil. It is an animal. We can say the same of the villagers. They're merely following rules.

Plus, it's my best fap material.

This read definitely gives off one of those weird dark cultist mood. The art was too pretty for its own good, it lightens up the mood when it shouldn't. There could of been more panels paying attention to the horrific dissecting which could of made it a lot more creepier, also the clean body cuts cancels out the moment of pain and agony that should put the viewers on edge. I hate how the mood turned lighter at the end of the ritual, made it seem like this is beautiful and okay when it really isn't although I may be wrong about that (I believe the lighter mood shows the perspective of the opposition's point of view). The weirdest part about this has to be the cock ritual part, seemed like a joke (Though I'm sure people actually do this shit anyway). And to top off this thriller, we have a curveball ending. 5/10 read *note: seemed like pretty generic horror story with the art being its greatess strength in beauty while at the same time being its greatest weakness in potraying horror.
